Fishery,  75  JOURNAL OF POLITICAL ECONOMY 124  (1954);  Garrett  Hardin,  The  Tragedy  of  the 
Commons, 162 SCIENCE 1243 (1968); and James Sanchirico and Susan Hanna, Navigating U.S. 
Fishery Policy into the 21st Century, 19 MARINE RESOURCE ECONOMICS 395 (2004). 

