» The  Pacific  Whiting  Cooperative  reported  lower  rates  of  bycatch  post  imple-
mentation.25 Whether the reduction is due to the formation of the cooperative, 
however, is not clear as the other non-coop sectors have also seen a decline.26 
» Annual  trades  or  leases  of  catches  for  the  median  fish  stock  are  on  the  order 
of  40  percent  of  the  total  allowable  catch  in  New  Zealand,  30  percent  in  Ice-
