Senator CANTWELL. Could the two of you comment on the House 

language on vessel replacement and your thoughts? 

Ms.  PARKER.  Madam  Chair,  there  are  three  components  here. 
Any  replaced  vessel  is  prohibited  from  participating  in  any  fishery 
outside the North Pacific and the West Coast hake fishery. Any re-
built  or  replaced  vessel  that  increases  its  length  would  be  prohib-
ited from fishing in the Gulf of Alaska. And any retired AFA vessel 

