As  I  commented  in  my  testimony,  though,  with  respect  to  the 
catcher/processor  sector  of  the  AFA  fleet,  it  is  not  a  safety  issue. 
Nearly  all  of  the  vessels  are  classed  and  all  the  vessels  are  load- 
